The ActivitySource and Meter instances should be disposed properly. Consider implementing IDisposable on the class or using a static factory pattern with proper disposal handling.
```suggestion
    private static readonly Meter MeterSource = new("WEX.Benefits.Persons.Importer");
    private static bool _disposed = false;

    /// <summary>
    /// Disposes static ActivitySource and MeterSource. Should be called during application shutdown.
    /// </summary>
    public static void Dispose()
    {
        if (!_disposed)
        {
            ActivitySource.Dispose();
            MeterSource.Dispose();
            _disposed = true;
        }
    }
```

